\fIsource\fR
parameter can also be omitted if
\fB$LINGUAS_FILE\fR
is set\&.
.sp
Target nodes defined through
\fBPOInit\fR
are not built by default (they\*(Aqre
Ignored from
\*(Aq\&.\*(Aq
node) but are added to special
\fBAlias\fR
(\*(Aqpo\-create\*(Aq
by default)\&. The alias name may be changed through the
\fB$POCREATE_ALIAS\fR
