.RS 4
.\}
.nf
# POTFILES\&.in in \*(Aqpo/\*(Aq subdirectory
\&.\&./a\&.cpp
\&.\&./b\&.cpp
# end of file
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.sp
The name of the file (POTFILES\&.in) containing the list of sources is provided via
\fB$XGETTEXTFROM\fR:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
# SConstruct file in \*(Aqpo/\*(Aq subdirectory
