\fB$LIBPREFIX\fR
construction variable
(by default,
lib
on POSIX systems, nothing on Windows systems), and suffix, specified by the
\fB$LIBSUFFIX\fR
construction variable
(by default,
\&.lib
on Windows systems,
\&.a
on POSIX systems), are automatically added to the target if not already present\&. Example:
