which sets the path to the JSON file created when
\-\-debug=json
is set\&.
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
DebugOptions(json=\*(Aq#/build/output/scons_stats\&.json\*(Aq)
.fi
.if n \{\
