\fIaffect_signature\fR
flag which will wrap non\-empty returned value with $( and $) to indicate the contents should not affect the signature of the generated command line\&.
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
        env[\*(Aq_CPPINCFLAGS\*(Aq] = \*(Aq${_concat(INCPREFIX, CPPPATH, INCSUFFIX, __env__, RDirs, TARGET, SOURCE, affect_signature=False)}\*(Aq
    
