will not use the contents of the value of
\fB$JAVACLASSPATH\fR
when searching for sources\&.
.sp .5v
.RE
.RE
.PP
\fBJAVACLASSSUFFIX\fR
.RS 4
The suffix for Java class files;
\&.class
by default\&.
